Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.61,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,讓人想要逃避的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:34.45,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,無論是誰都會遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.45,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,但是 勇敢面對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.87,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.79,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,胸中想要守護的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.71,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.63,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,未來就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.84,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,等待著那些閃光的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:55.18,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,甩開淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:01:00.18,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,向這片天空起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:03.52,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,來吧 揮動翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.60,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,鼓起無敵的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:09.52,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,不再猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:12.28,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:14.99,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,用力伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:19.95,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,向著誰都不曾知曉的那片天空
