Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:28.11,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,把自己的價值觀強加於人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:31.16,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,-15)}又倍感痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:40.46,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,儘管如此 我們也要生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:46.71,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,就算受傷 就算流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:51.97,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,明天也仍將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:57.56,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,不要哭泣 無論到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:02.98,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,我們也會面對
